      <title>墨西哥就厄瓜多尔突袭大使馆事件提出抗议，寻求联合国裁决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/mexico-seeks-un-ruling-in-protest-of-ecuador-s-raid-of-embassy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[厄瓜多尔警方冲进墨西哥驻厄瓜多尔大使馆逮捕一名寻求庇护的高级政客后，墨西哥将向联合国正式起诉厄瓜多尔，两国关系急转直下。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/mexico-seeks-un-ruling-in-protest-of-ecuador-s-raid-of-embassy</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 22:15:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国在海上的大规模建设令菲律宾在小岛的扩张相形见绌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/china-s-huge-sea-buildup-dwarfs-philippine-push-on-tiny-island</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南中国海的一个小岛象征着这场斗争——和差距——与中国相比，菲律宾在争议水域主张其权利的努力，中国对大部分水域拥有主权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/china-s-huge-sea-buildup-dwarfs-philippine-push-on-tiny-island</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>医生短缺造成的死亡加剧了韩国的选举焦虑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/deaths-from-doctor-shortage-fuel-election-angst-in-south-korea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2023 年 3 月，韩国大邱市一名 17 岁女孩从一栋大楼坠落，救护车被三家缺乏医生救治的医院拒之门外后死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/deaths-from-doctor-shortage-fuel-election-angst-in-south-korea</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>图斯克的联盟赢得波兰地方选举以增强权力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/tusk-s-coalition-wins-local-elections-in-poland-to-bolster-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理唐纳德·图斯克领导的执政联盟有望赢得波兰地方选举，这对于他的四个月政府来说是一场苦乐参半的胜利，该政府寻求修复与欧盟的紧张关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/tusk-s-coalition-wins-local-elections-in-poland-to-bolster-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 19:58:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登盟友反对停止美国向以色列转让武器</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/biden-ally-opposes-halting-us-weapons-transfers-to-israel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登总统的参议院盟友表示，美国应继续向以色列运送武器，他拒绝了众议院议员的呼吁，即在对以色列导弹袭击导致加沙七名世界中央厨房援助人员死亡的事件进行全面调查之前暂停武器转让。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/biden-ally-opposes-halting-us-weapons-transfers-to-israel</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 16:09:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多为加拿大人工智能行业推出 18 亿加元一揽子计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/trudeau-unveils-1-8-billion-plan-to-boost-ai-sector-in-canada</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着总理贾斯汀·特鲁多继续在新预算之前发布支出公告，加拿大正在启动一项基金来促进其人工智能行业的发展，并创建一个新的人工智能安全研究所。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/trudeau-unveils-1-8-billion-plan-to-boost-ai-sector-in-canada</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 15:51:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
