      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 10:59:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>内塔尼亚胡称胜利临近，从加沙撤军</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/war-in-middle-east-israel-has-responses-ready-for-iran-scenarios</link>
      <description><![CDATA[军方官员周日表示，以色列正在从加沙南部的汗尤尼斯撤出部分部队，并称随着针对哈马斯的战争进入六个月大关，以色列已经结束了在那里的任务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/war-in-middle-east-israel-has-responses-ready-for-iran-scenarios</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 08:48:26 GMT</pubDate>
